01:10:22.391 --> 01:10:25.103
We were racing most closely
with the Ganassi cars.


1535
01:10:25.603 --> 01:10:29.648
[announcer] <i>Last year's winner,
the 10 car of Dario Franchitti.</i>


1536
01:10:29.649 --> 01:10:31.108
<i>Number 9 with Scott Dixon.</i>

1537
01:10:31.109 --> 01:10:33.861
<i>He is the favorite
