01:10:51.629 --> 01:10:53.172
<i>[Bryan] There was a caution,</i>

1546
01:10:54.298 --> 01:10:55.966
<i>and the leaders all pitted.</i>

1547
01:10:55.967 --> 01:10:58.635
[announcer 1] <i>Dario Franchitti
