01:11:02.390 --> 01:11:05.852
[announcer 1] <i>They're trying
to make this in this last stop.</i>


1551
01:11:08.020 --> 01:11:09.647
[Bryan] And I've got
a decision to make.


1552
01:11:10.064 --> 01:11:12.149
Either we pit with the leaders

1553
01:11:12.150 --> 01:11:15.485
and try and bring home
a solid top-five finish,


1554
01:11:15.486 --> 01:11:17.738
or we risk it all...

1555
01:11:18.531 --> 01:11:19.991
and go for a win.

1556
01:11:21.492 --> 01:11:23.035
And we stayed out.

1557
01:11:23.453 --> 01:11:25.579
[announcer 2] <i>Dan Wheldon's
saying, "This is the 500,</i>


1558
01:11:25.580 --> 01:11:27.248
<i>I'm not gonna give it up."</i>

1559
01:11:29.333 --> 01:11:32.461
[Bryan] We made our pit stop
a little bit later,


1560
01:11:32.462 --> 01:11:34.297
where we didn't
have to save fuel.


1561
01:11:34.672 --> 01:11:36.339
[engine revving]

1562
01:11:36.340 --> 01:11:39.509
And we were running hard
at the end of that race,


1563
01:11:39.510 --> 01:11:41.136
chasing everybody down.

1564
01:11:41.137 --> 01:11:43.181
[engines revving]

