1570
01:12:04.786 --> 01:12:08.079
<i>The 10 car of Dario Franchitti.</i>

1571
01:12:08.080 --> 01:12:09.873
<i>But it's gonna be
very tight on fuel.</i>


1572
01:12:09.874 --> 01:12:11.375
I was in the fight.

