01:13:03.845 --> 01:13:06.597
[announcer 1]
<i>The white flag is in hand.</i>


1595
01:13:07.014 --> 01:13:08.932
<i>Through the final two corners.</i>

1596
01:13:08.933 --> 01:13:11.977
<i>Dan Wheldon's chances
