1611
01:13:43.134 --> 01:13:45.469
[dramatic string music builds]

1612
01:13:45.470 --> 01:13:48.014
[muffled crowd reaction]

1613
01:13:48.473 --> 01:13:50.057
[gasping]

1614
01:13:55.605 --> 01:13:59.484
[string music swells]

1615
01:14:01.694 --> 01:14:04.864
[announcer 1] <i>Dan Wheldon
is going to win the race!</i>


1616
01:14:08.993 --> 01:14:10.619
Wait a sec, did he get it?

1617
01:14:10.620 --> 01:14:13.663
- Yeah!
