1618
01:14:13.664 --> 01:14:16.667
Oh, my God. Oh, my God.

1619
01:14:17.168 --> 01:14:19.587
I can remember hearing
him on the radio say...


1620
01:14:22.340 --> 01:14:24.425
[announcer 1]
<i>That is unbelievable.</i>


1621
01:14:24.842 --> 01:14:26.511
Oh, my God.

1622
01:14:26.886 --> 01:14:28.096
Oh, my God!

1623
01:14:28.596 --> 01:14:33.016
[announcer 1] <i>Wheldon wins when
J. R. Hildebrand hits the wall.</i>


1624
01:14:33.017 --> 01:14:34.643
[announcer 2] <i>One of the most
