[crying]

2103
01:40:20.481 --> 01:40:22.024
[sobbing]

2104
01:40:35.746 --> 01:40:39.667
[sobbing]

2105
01:40:42.920 --> 01:40:45.465
["About Today"
by The National playing]


2106
01:40:59.479 --> 01:41:01.022
<i>♪ Today ♪</i>

2107
01:41:06.819 --> 01:41:09.280
<i>♪ You were far away... ♪</i>

2108
01:41:09.822 --> 01:41:11.531
[Michael] We were ready
to sign a contract


2109
01:41:11.532 --> 01:41:13.450
the day that he died.
It was all done.


2110
01:41:13.451 --> 01:41:14.659
It was all agreed upon.

